?m=1695370146", "stars": 3208, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 615650, "username": "oColtono", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/oColtono", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03d17d94f59f8179270d3287c21eb1ca?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03d17d94f59f8179270d3287c21eb1ca?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03d17d94f59f8179270d3287c21eb1ca?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1677122124, "last_modified": 1682236282}, "last_reply_by": "EndlessMemory", "last_touched": 1724205478, "title": "🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻我是个小公司桌面运维，老板让我给他开发个 AI 大模型……", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066362", "created": 1724123042, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题\r\n我在一家非 IT 行业的公司干桌面运维，说是运维其实啥都干，简单的服务器运维、直播推流、摄影摄像等等。老板基本上是个技术盲，在他眼里，技术相关的问题我全知道。\r\n\r\n他想要有一个 AI ，把一位哲学家（比较小众）的文集通读一遍（大概 40 万字）。然后扮演这位哲学家，充当聊天机器人。这个聊天机器人的用户量估计不会太高（小众圈子里面流传一下），最多也就 1000 人左右（并发可能就 30 人以内）。\r\n\r\n我说我干不来，他表示让我至少给个方案，适当招两个人，或者找人外包都行。\r\n\r\n从头搞个 AI 模型我猜是不可能的，我大概想法是租个云服务器，给 Llama 3 或类似的开源模型喂点数据，然后套个前端。\r\n\r\n希望懂行的朋友告诉我一下我的想法是否可行？以及这个事情工作量大不大。如果可行的话，我就去着手研究一下怎样微调 Llama 3 ，然后给老板一个方案。", "content_rendered": "如题<br />我在一家非 IT 行业的公司干桌面运维，说是运维其实啥都干，简单的服务器运维、直播推流、摄影摄像等等。老板基本上是个技术盲，在他眼里，技术相关的问题我全知道。<br /><br />他想要有一个 AI ，把一位哲学家（比较小众）的文集通读一遍（大概 40 万字）。然后扮演这位哲学家，充当聊天机器人。这个聊天机器人的用户量估计不会太高（小众圈子里面流传一下），最多也就 1000 人左右（并发可能就 30 人以内）。<br /><br />我说我干不来，他表示让我至少给个方案，适当招两个人，或者找人外包都行。<br /><br />从头搞个 AI 模型我猜是不可能的，我大概想法是租个云服务器，给 Llama 3 或类似的开源模型喂点数据，然后套个前端。<br /><br />希望懂行的朋友告诉我一下我的想法是否可行？以及这个事情工作量大不大。如果可行的话，我就去着手研究一下怎样微调 Llama 3 ，然后给老板一个方案。", "last_modified": 1724151134, "replies": 98, "id": 1066362}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_large.png?m=1605263518", "name": "browsers", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_normal.png?m=1605263518", "title": "浏览器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/browsers", "topics": 723, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Browsers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_mini.png?m=1605263518", "stars": 430, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 422, "parent_node_name": "software"}, "member": {"id": 657012, "username": "drymonfidelia", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/drymonfidelia", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1698662217, "last_modified": 1722203860}, "last_reply_by": "yakun4566", "last_touched": 1724205339, "title": "逆天 Chrome，新版本连下载链接都不让看了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066450", "created": 1724138159, "deleted": 0, "content": "![new-chrome]( https://i.imgur.com/MExdgl3.png)\r\n\r\n点开链接只会打开 https://github.com\r\n\r\n虽然可以从 dev tools 看到实际下载链接，但有的网站下载链接是 js 调用 window.open 打开的，就看不到\r\n\r\n我也很想转 firefox ，但实在太拉跨了，在 bugzilla 反馈过几个 bug ，他们员工也都复现出来了，但是半年多了就是不修，现在只能备用 esr 版 firefox ，正式版 firefox 每天 crash", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"new-chrome\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MExdgl3.png\"/></p>\n<p>点开链接只会打开 <a href=\"https://github.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com</a></p>\n<p>虽然可以从 dev tools 看到实际下载链接，但有的网站下载链接是 js 调用 window.open 打开的，就看不到</p>\n<p>我也很想转 firefox ，但实在太拉跨了，在 bugzilla 反馈过几个 bug ，他们员工也都复现出来了，但是半年多了就是不修，现在只能备用 esr 版 firefox ，正式版 firefox 每天 crash</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724151461, "replies": 84, "id": 1066450}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 2294, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1929, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 345913, "username": "zhengdutech", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhengdutech", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_mini.png?m=1539400694", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_normal.png?m=1539400694", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_large.png?m=1539400694", "created": 1535679428, "last_modified": 1539400694}, "last_reply_by": "thfurior", "last_touched": 1724175308, "title": "来群懂哥帮我分析下我目前的情况该买个什么车？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066410", "created": 1724133039, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：29 岁，有车有房有老婆有一孩，房贷 2500 一个月(之前提前还贷了)，开了 8 年的马自达昂克赛拉，目前存款现金 50w 多一点点。家庭年收入大概 40 个。\r\n\r\n我一直以来的梦想就是宝马三系，实在是想买，年轻的时候预算不足才上的马 3 ，而且我还想买个二手的，f 地盘 E48 发动机的 320Li 曜夜版的，二手也就 15w 左右，最近看过很多款，就能实现我的梦想。我是真喜欢宝马。\r\n\r\n但是考虑家庭情况，是否需要一次到位换个理想 L6 ？兼顾家庭，主要让老婆孩子坐的舒服，但是说实话冰箱彩电大沙发并不是我的刚需。\r\n\r\n\r\n理想 L6 需要 28w ，二手 3 系 15w 就能到手，我的车还能卖个 3 万多一点。\r\n\r\n兄弟们，我是应该坚持我的宝马梦还是上理想？", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：29 岁，有车有房有老婆有一孩，房贷 2500 一个月(之前提前还贷了)，开了 8 年的马自达昂克赛拉，目前存款现金 50w 多一点点。家庭年收入大概 40 个。</p>\n<p>我一直以来的梦想就是宝马三系，实在是想买，年轻的时候预算不足才上的马 3 ，而且我还想买个二手的，f 地盘 E48 发动机的 320Li 曜夜版的，二手也就 15w 左右，最近看过很多款，就能实现我的梦想。我是真喜欢宝马。</p>\n<p>但是考虑家庭情况，是否需要一次到位换个理想 L6 ？兼顾家庭，主要让老婆孩子坐的舒服，但是说实话冰箱彩电大沙发并不是我的刚需。</p>\n<p>理想 L6 需要 28w ，二手 3 系 15w 就能到手，我的车还能卖个 3 万多一点。</p>\n<p>兄弟们，我是应该坚持我的宝马梦还是上理想？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724149748, "replies": 72, "id": 1066410}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1611920927", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1611920927", "title": "游戏", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/games", "topics": 2773, "footer": "", "header": "Life is short, have more fun.", "title_alternative": "Games", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927", "stars": 2402, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 55, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 279756, "username": "name68", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/name68", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/177f2c82b6bf48bc15a0d84052380ad7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/177f2c82b6bf48bc15a0d84052380ad7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/177f2c82b6bf48bc15a0d84052380ad7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1515067156, "last_modified": 1720006322}, "last_reply_by": "Deidra", "last_touched": 1724185999, "title": "黑神话悟空热度真高,想玩,但是我晕 3d,怎么解?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066421", "created": 1724134468, "deleted": 0, "content": "难不成还要吃着晕车药玩儿", "content_rendered": "难不成还要吃着晕车药玩儿", "last_modified": 1724150136, "replies": 65, "id": 1066421}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 11719, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5891, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 50725, "username": "finalshot", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/finalshot", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a62e/2571/50725_mini.png?m=1723369024", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a62e/2571/50725_normal.png?m=1723369024", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a62e/2571/50725_large.png?m=1723369024", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a62e/2571/50725_xlarge.png?m=1723369024", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a62e/2571/50725_xlarge.png?m=1723369024", "created": 1385531680, "last_modified": 1723369024}, "last_reply_by": "QAQGan", "last_touched": 1724177098, "title": "有什么推荐的 Android 性价比手机？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066367", "created": 1724123488, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前主力机是 iPhone 15 Pro Max ，想买一台 Android 机做备用机器，我的需求是：\r\n- 能够稳定使用 Google 全家桶，tg ，x 等，可绑定 Google Play 做内购。\r\n- 稳定安全和流畅\r\n- 偶尔打打电话或者刷刷视频之类的，出门旅游当备用机\r\n- 预算 3k 左右，如果比这个少那更好啦\r\n\r\n目前看下来 iQOO 12 好像推荐的人比较多，有没有其他可推荐的？感谢", "content_rendered": "<p>目前主力机是 iPhone 15 Pro Max ，想买一台 Android 机做备用机器，我的需求是：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>能够稳定使用 Google 全家桶，tg ，x 等，可绑定 Google Play 做内购。</li>\n<li>稳定安全和流畅</li>\n<li>偶尔打打电话或者刷刷视频之类的，出门旅游当备用机</li>\n<li>预算 3k 左右，如果比这个少那更好啦</li>\n</ul>\n<p>目前看下来 iQOO 12 好像推荐的人比较多，有没有其他可推荐的？感谢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724123524, "replies": 58, "id": 1066367}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_large.png?m=1651386010", "name": "wechat", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_normal.png?m=1651386010", "title": "微信", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/wechat", "topics": 3857, "footer": "", "header": "关于微信及微信小程序的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "WeChat", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_mini.png?m=1651386010", "stars": 754, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 649, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 381640, "username": "DIMOJANG", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/DIMOJANG", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/83a8/01e3/381640_mini.png?m=17